snippet.title: Hardest Game - Ez Edition (Trailer)
snippet.description:
Link - https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.knights.hardestgame
Link - https://knights-game.itch.io/hardest-game-ez-edition

You are the CUTE SQUARE, and you need to find the portal in order to proceed to the next levels, but many enemies are coming to your way that will try to defeat you. Avoid them to survive, and go to the next level.


#WorldHardestGameEver #NewGame #HardestGameEver
